de.mdelab.comparch

Interface PerformanceStats

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchitecturalElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PerformanceStatsImpl

    public interface PerformanceStats
extends ArchitecturalElement
    A representation of the model object 'Performance Stats'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Min Time
    • Max Time
    • Total Time
    • Invocation Count
    • Interface
    • Method
    See Also:
    ComparchPackage.getPerformanceStats()
